SYSTEM: Wiki: https://delicias.dia.fi.upm.es/wiki/index.php/Stanfordjan2011 

The National Center for Biomedical Ontology at the Stanford University School of Medicine has a position open for a Senior Software Engineer with experience working with Semantic Web tools. Experience using one or more open source triple stores would be a big plus.
For much more information about the position, and to apply, please go to :
http://jobs.stanford.edu/find_a_job.html
and do a “keyword search” on the job id “40126”.
speaker: SYSTEM
